These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-8-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, orchid, daffodil
City: hannover, nizza, new-york
House: wooden, modern, gothic-revival
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade, 7up
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, photography, reading
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, train, trike
 1. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hannover##5
 2. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the gothic-revival house##8
 3. the person who growsdaffodil is not to the left of the modern house##8
 4. the wooden house is the person who's hobby is reading##1
 5. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person driving the airplane##5
 6. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
 7. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##5
 8. the person driving the train is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
 9. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaffodil##5
10. the person driving the train is not to the left of the person drinking lemonade##8
11. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1
12. the person drinking 7up is not to the right of the person traveling to nizza##8
13. the person drinking 7up is somewhere between the gothic-revival house and the person who growsdahlia##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Flower          | dahlia | orchid | daffodil    |
| City           | hannover | nizza   | new-york     |
| House   | wooden     | modern   | gothic-revival       |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | 7up   | cola     |
| Hobby   | reading    | hiking   | photography |
| Transport     | trike     | airplane | train     |

