 3. the person drinking soy-milk is the vegafina-smoker##1
 4. the aristoff-smoker is not to the right of the person traveling to colone##8
 5. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the vegafina-smoker##5
 6. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the aristoff-smoker##3
 7. the person drinking fanta is not to the right of the person traveling to colone##8
 8. the wooden house is somewhere to the right of the firefighter##5
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
10. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
11. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the accountant##1
12. the victorian house is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##8
13. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to miami##5
14. the accountant is the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
