 4. the vegafina-smoker is not the owner of the rat##6
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is not to the right of the person who growssunflower##8
 6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
 7. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the wooden house##5
 9. the person who likes azure is in the middle##1
10. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the right of the wooden house##5
11. the vegafina-smoker is not to the left of the chaman-smoker##8

