.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-8-16::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, mirinda
There 3 different types of food: grapefruit, cranberry, eggplant
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, yellow, chestnut
3 different pets are kept: fish, pony, turtle
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, rose, tulip
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, d&b, classical
 1. the owner of the fish is not the fan of d&b##6
 2. the owner of the pony is not to the right of the person eating grapefruit##8
 3. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
 4. the person who growstulip is not the fan of classical##6
 5. the person drinking mirinda is between the person eating cranberry and the person who growsrose##2
 6. the fan of punk is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 7. the person drinking 7up is not to the left of the person eating cranberry##8
 8. the person who likes chestnut is somewhere between the person drinking cola and the person eating cranberry##7
 9. the person who likes apricot is not the person drinking mirinda##6
10. the fan of d&b is between the owner of the fish and the fan of classical##2
11. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
12. the person eating eggplant is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |     3     |
| Beverage      | 7up       | mirinda         | cola      |
| Food         | cranberry     | eggplant         | grapefruit    |
| Color           | apricot  | chestnut | yellow |
| Pet   | fish    | pony        | turtle      |
| Flower         | tulip  | begonia        | rose    |
| Music-Genre     | punk | d&b      | classical      |

