.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-8-17::.
City: prague, berlin, edinburgh
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, parkour, rowing
The people have 3 different jobs:  firefighter, paramedic, videographer
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, orange, mauve
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, aconite, tulip
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, motorbike, quad-bike
 1. the firefighter is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
 2. the person who likes mauve is not the person driving the motorbike##6
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the left of the person who growsaconite##5
 4. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to prague##5
 5. the person who's sport is parkour is not the person who likes brown##6
 6. the person who growstulip is the person who likes brown##1
 7. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the right of the paramedic##5
 8. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
 9. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
10. the person driving the subway is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
11. the person who likes mauve is in an odd position##4
12. the person who likes orange is not to the left of the person driving the motorbike##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| City      | edinburgh     | berlin | prague |
| Sport         | rowing   | parkour       | cycling       |
| Job           | paramedic | videographer  | firefighter |
| Color   | mauve   | orange         | brown       |
| Flower   | daffodil   | aconite     | tulip        |
| Transport           | subway       | motorbike       | quad-bike    |

