.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-8-18::.
House: futuristic, cape-cod, ranch-style
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, social-worker, software-developer
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, yellow, ebony
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, july, december
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, hip-hop, salsa
City: hannover, marseilles, london
 1. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 2. the person who likes ebony is the ranch-style house##1
 3. the social-worker is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the left of the fan of hip-hop##5
 5. the person traveling to hannover is not to the left of the person traveling to london##8
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the left of the person who likes yellow##8
 7. the cape-cod house is not to the left of the software-developer##8
 8. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 9. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
10. the fan of salsa is between the fan of disco and the person who's birthday is in july##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2      |       3       |
| House          | cape-cod         | futuristic     | ranch-style        |
| Job           | software-developer | doctor     | social-worker |
| Color   | blood-red           | yellow  | ebony          |
| Birthday           | december               | march | july       |
| Music-Genre         | disco           | salsa | hip-hop    |
| City     | london               | hannover        | marseilles       |

