.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-8-19::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, yellow, blue
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, havana, pall-mall
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, epic, musical
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, goat, rat
3 different games are played: backgammon, snooker, bridge
City: venice, rome, hannover
 1. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
 2. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 3. the person who likes yellow is not to the left of the siglo-smoker##8
 4. the siglo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the pall-mall-smoker##5
 5. the person playing backgammon is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the siglo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the pall-mall-smoker##5
 7. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 8. the owner of the rat is between the havana-smoker and the pall-mall-smoker##2
 9. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
10. the person who likes blue is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to rome##5
11. the owner of the goat is not to the right of the havana-smoker##8
12. the person watching musical movies is somewhere between the person traveling to venice and the person traveling to rome##7
13. the person traveling to hannover is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3       |
| Color          | azure  | blue | yellow       |
| Cigar         | pall-mall | siglo    | havana      |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | musical    | comedy       |
| Pet   | goat   | rat        | goldfish        |
| Game         | backgammon  | snooker     | bridge |
| City     | rome | hannover        | venice         |

