.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-8-20::.
There 3 different types of food: apple, lettuce, orange
House: townhouse, colonial, cottage
There are 3 different nationalities: british, italian, polish
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, ship, tram
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, siglo, vegafina
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk, cola
 1. the person driving the motorbike is not to the left of the person drinking 7up##8
 2. the person drinking milk is the italian##1
 3. the person drinking cola is not to the left of the person eating apple##8
 4. the british is the person eating apple##1
 5. the person driving the ship is not to the right of the italian##8
 6. the british is the siglo-smoker##1
 7. the person driving the motorbike is not to the left of the cottage house##8
 8. the polish is somewhere to the right of the montecristo-smoker##5
 9. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
10. the colonial house is not to the left of the cottage house##8
11. the montecristo-smoker is in an odd position##4
12. the italian is not to the right of the person driving the tram##8
13. the person driving the tram is the colonial house##1
14. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the polish##3
15. the person eating orange is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Food          | lettuce   | apple     | orange       |
| House           | cottage | townhouse    | colonial |
| Nationality   | italian   | british | polish          |
| Transport   | ship     | motorbike   | tram      |
| Cigar           | montecristo       | siglo     | vegafina        |
| Beverage         | milk   | 7up  | cola      |

 